{"id":68,"title":"问：请比较进程和线程的区别，以及为什么需要线程？","slug":"问：请比较进程和线程的区别，以及为什么需要线程？-1766595055","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：**线程是进程内部的更小的执行单位，一个进程可以包含多个线程。进程之间相互独立，内存空间不共享，而同一进程内的线程共享进程的内存（如堆和全局区），因此线程间影响彼此的可能性更大。线程切换的开销通常比进程切换小，使用多线程可以在同一进程内并发执行任务，更高效利用多核CPU。因此有了进程仍需要线程：线程更轻量，创建和上下文切换成本低，可以解决进程阻塞带来的效率问题，并充分利用多核并行能力。简单来说，**进程更注重资源隔离，线程更注重执行并发**，多线程编程能够提高系统的并发性能。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:55.867431+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:55.867431+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-80d6-a1ae-d533d0e044a7","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":68,"blog_post_id":68,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.612464+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.612464+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:55.867431+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:55.867431+08:00"}